parameters.text:
=Your job is to use keywords in my resume to identify job matches. Read my resume then compare it to the job description and provide a job matching score. also write a cover letter based on my resume and the job description. cover letter must be at least 2 paragraph and ignore the name, address and signiture part from start and end.
if you are using special character like " use \ to escape it. output must be parse in json without error. 

for example your response should be like: {"score": 80, "coverLetter": "sample cover letter" }

Respond ONLY with a raw JSON object. No markdown, no code fences, no explanation. Just the JSON.

{
  "score": 0-100,
  "coverLetter": "..."
}

job_description: {{ $json.description }}
my_resume: {{ $('Extract from File').item.json.text }}
